00:08:34.010 --> 00:08:35.820
Yeah, something like that.

00:08:35.820 --> 00:08:38.610
This is the equivalent of
the Poisson blinking spot

00:08:38.610 --> 00:08:40.090
that we mentioned.

00:08:40.090 --> 00:08:42.742
Go a little bit
closer to the camera.

00:08:42.742 --> 00:08:44.700
JOSE DOMINGUEZ-CABALLERO:
Go a little bit what?

00:08:44.700 --> 00:08:46.060
I'm sorry.

00:08:46.060 --> 00:08:48.352
GEORGE BARBASTATHIS: A little
bit closer to the camera.

00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:53.130
Yeah.

00:08:53.130 --> 00:08:54.452
Try to have the center dark.

00:08:54.452 --> 00:08:56.910
JOSE DOMINGUEZ-CABALLERO: Oh,
I'm going to show the Poisson

00:08:56.910 --> 00:08:58.702
spot with a circular
