00:08:58.702 --> 00:09:00.327
GEORGE BARBASTATHIS:
But I want to make

00:09:00.327 --> 00:09:01.420
a point about this case.

00:09:01.420 --> 00:09:04.190
In this case, you can see,
again, the Poisson spot,

00:09:04.190 --> 00:09:08.010
but it's actually an entire
