00:27:24.680 --> 00:27:29.250
So this grating has a
very, very small period.

00:27:29.250 --> 00:27:31.530
The contrast I picked
to be 1 in this case,

00:27:31.530 --> 00:27:33.880
and there's no phase shift.

00:27:33.880 --> 00:27:37.030
So I will play the movie now,
